Goals contain contextual variables gathered by requirements.  These make
actions modular and can be specialize to a particular task by changing
the goal's requirement(s).

block: The name of the block desired to obtain
 - Breaking
 - Crafting
 - Placing
 - Transfering
pos: The position being targeted.
 - Turtle movement
 - Building/plot position
turtle: The turtle in context
 - Can be a turtle to perform actions with or take actions on
item: The name of the item desired to obtain
 - Crafting
 - Using
 - Transfering
